import Header from "../components/Header"


const Nooty = () => {
    return <>
    <Header/>

    <form style={{textAlign: "center"}}>
        <input style={{width: "200px", height: "40px"}} type="text" placeholder="Enter Item"></input>
        <button>Add Item</button>
    </form>
    </>
}

export default Nooty
